{
  "stem": "15938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They weren't anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they were-- they were very, very kind to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, they were also limited for what they were allowed to do because officially, they took your business away, they took your land away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- so they couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then 1939, they just had to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that I remember was very sad because I had some Czech friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was not class 1, class 2.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually in one class, you had three-- three classes in one room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yes, that was still fine at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The pattern of education was repetition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to, you know, everything had to be by heart and repeated and repeated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And spelling was repeated and repeated until you knew it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, don't forget that in this class could be five, six people with different languages.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you had to learn it by heart because otherwise you couldn't cope with the class.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were children that only spoke Russian, children that only spoke Czech, children who only spoke Yiddish, and children who only spoke Hungarian because my parents spoke Hungarian at home because my mother always-- her mother language was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I don't think it stayed long enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that-- that kind of education doesn't remain with you because it changes so often that it's very hard to remember what, you know-- your memories should be from what you learned as a child.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our memory isn't because it wasn't solid enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then we went-- then after 1939, we weren't allowed to go to any non-Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we created a school, a Jewish school, so-called.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
